      "x": 270,
      "y": 96,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 158,
      "text": "How is it doing?\n\nGolden Signals:\n• Latency (p50/p95/p99)\n• Traffic (RPS)\n• Errors (error rate %)\n• Saturation (CPU, mem)\n\nAlert: p99 > 500ms\nAlert: error rate > 1%\nAlert: CPU > 80%\n\nStack: Prometheus\n+ Grafana + AlertMgr",
