      "text": "Where did time go?\n\nTrace ID: abc-123\nAPI Gateway  ██ 5ms\n└─ Auth      ███ 12ms\n└─ Cart      ████████ 250ms\n     └─DB    ███████ 220ms\n              ↑ BOTTLENECK!\n└─ Payment   ██ 8ms\n\nStack: Jaeger, Zipkin\nDatadog APM, AWS X-Ray\nStandard: OpenTelemetry",
